Package com.algonquincollege.cst8284.assignment2.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attack
    This abstract class represents an Attack a that character generates and contains a damage score.
    AttackReport
    This class contains two pieces of information, the first is a text-based description of how a character defended against an attack, the second is the actualDamage the character received, note that actualDamage could have a negative value indicating healing.
    BasicAttack
    This class represents a Basic attack that a character generates.
    Character
    This class represents a Character prototype, suitable for use in a Role-Playing Game.
    FireAttack
    This class represents a Fire attack that a character generates.
    FrostAttack
    This class represents a Frost attack that a character generates.
    MutantEagle
    This class represents a Mutant Eagle as combat character It is a subclass of the character class
    SeaMonster
    This class represents a Sea Monster as combat character It is a subclass of the Character class
